{"tid":431802,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【淫狼現晒形】「有反應」性愛機械人參展 畀人玩到手都斷","createTime":"2017-10-11T04:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T08:38:06.000Z","uid":117934,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6c92defd63e1c9e422054cc978c510bdb8085c","tid":431802,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"奧地利林茲（Linz）早前舉行藝術電子節，會上展出一部懂得回應人的觸碰及說話的性愛機械人，未料入場人士行為野蠻，令「她」飽受摧殘，要再入廠維修。<br />\n<br />\n來自西班牙的桑托斯（Sergi Santos）早前帶著性愛機械人「Samantha」到奧地利參展，「她」成為會上焦點。桑托斯形容入場人士行為野蠻，他說：「人們趴上『Samantha』的胸部、雙腿及雙臂。（『Samantha』）兩隻手指斷了，非常骯髒。人可以很壞，因為他們不明白這個科技，又不用付錢，他們對待『Samantha』的方式，十足野蠻人一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n身價3,700歐元（約3.4萬港元）的「Samantha」多才多藝，例如能對觸碰作出回應、擁抱、呻吟及記住曾與「她」「交流過」的人。在人工智能軟件協助下，「Samantha」能操多國語言，並有能力學習新事物。在雙峰被觸摸時，「Samantha」會呻吟及有所反應，而在「較頻密的性愛下」，「她」有能力模仿女性的性高潮。<br />\n<br />\n桑托斯要把「Samantha」寄回西班牙清潔及維修，他說：「『Samantha』承受能力高，『她』會捱得過的。」"},{"pid":"4b595d2f34e11fd24a38897afe8793eb3dfd7854","tid":431802,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170928/large/1506563462_820e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170928%2Flarge%2F1506563462_820e.jpg&h=25121a8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"921023cdd5cbfeea33fa9e0d2f69ad345eddaa7f","tid":431802,"uid":117934,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.limitlessiq.com/media/wysiwyg/20170807/sergi-santos-sex-robot-1031161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fwysiwyg%2F20170807%2Fsergi-santos-sex-robot-1031161.jpg&h=7f5691ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae8729a90f8108aa5cc42f43ea4fdbd003aa9cd2","tid":431802,"uid":3549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T08:38:06.000Z","msg":"她知道 哭是沒有用的"}]}